{"tid":1631991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特區政府嚴厲譴責連日暴力行為！！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:54:41.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e24ee8e647019e706ab44a248dfdffc9699ceb02","tid":1631991,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEAtghX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEAtghX.png&h=b6a2a48b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】特區政府嚴厲譴責大批蒙面暴徒目無法紀的暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，連日的暴力行為令社會陷入恐慌和混亂，影響多項公共服務，商戶擔心受破壞暫停營業，市民擔心安全不敢外出。<br />\n<br />\n暴徒近日多次襲擊其他人，令受害者嚴重受傷，亦有記者被汽油彈燒傷，港鐵服務一度全面停頓，對市民生活構成嚴重不便。<br />\n<br />\n政府指，禁蒙面法已經生效，為防止進一步暴力和騷亂，讓香港恢復和平與穩定，呼籲市民不要以身試法。"},{"pid":"281c6c8e12e8d6bb83d5a183605675b022998900","tid":1631991,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"呢d要搵民間記者會拆掂佢"},{"pid":"48df5d7a06293a0c783de72ef1a773dab4621d6a","tid":1631991,"uid":292024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"記者都未撚出聲垃圾政府仲想搞分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15111bad14b0b5b7702ab0112ac74d457342cc5b","tid":1631991,"uid":165525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:53:50.000Z","msg":"佢琴日唔係話前日冇暴力 蒙面法好成功咩"},{"pid":"dbeeced9b57ddb5ba489c28c2d31831a73b94bc0","tid":1631991,"uid":57674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:54:41.000Z","msg":"又係講廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}